                     <interp inst="t18090920-75-off428" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090920-75-off428" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18090920-75-cd429" type="crimeDate">20th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-75-off428 t18090920-75-cd429"></join>, a watch, value 2 l. 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090920-75-victim713" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Kerwood
                        <interp inst="t18090920-75-victim713" type="surname" value="Kerwood"></interp>
